This Zap extension is a central repository for text-related Zap extension
commands which are not directly tied to a specific extension mode. If you
have comments on it, please direct them to the zap-devel mailing list.

The following have code used with permission in the Zap text extension:

	James Aylett		[maintainer]
	Martin Ebourne
	Justin Fletcher
	Paul Moore
	Darren Salt
	Dominic Symes
	Tim Tyler
	Daniel Wagenaar

You need Zap 1.42 or later to run ZapText.

